headline: 2 Reasons to Like WM (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Over the last six months, Waste Management’s shares have sunk to $209.00, producing a disappointing 10.8% loss - a stark contrast to the S&P 500’s 13.6% gain. This was partly due to its softer quarterly results and might have investors contemplating their next move.
